dct_description_sm: Map of Mantoloking on the Atlantic Ocean and Barnegat Bay. Mantoloking is part of Brick Township. Surveyed and laid out by R. C. Bacot of Jersey City, NJ, assisted by J. C. Payne. Small map in corner showing railroad lines into Mantoloking and surrounding towns.
